title: (Tues Early Bird) Artist Responds to Lunchbox’s Beef + Jillian Jaqueline + TJ Osbourne perform their new Duet + Amy and Lunchbox Compete in Cover Song Game
itunes:title: (Tues Early Bird) Artist Responds to Lunchbox’s Beef + Jillian Jaqueline + TJ Osbourne perform their new Duet + Amy and Lunchbox Compete in Cover Song Game
description:
The artist that Lunchbox has formed a beef with responds to his claims. Jillian Jaqueline + TJ Osbourne of Brothers Osborne come in to talk about their new duet and perform it. Amy and Lunchbox try to guess the original artist based on the famous cover.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
